divs: Sighting DetailsObject moving northeast from southwest. Bright white light no blinking. too low and too bright to be satellite. Moving in wrong direction to be satellite from this area. My wife also nwitnessed object and called me from 15 miles away. Object moved a bit slower than an aircraft, and in a direction aircraft do not normally follow in this area.
